heaviest_rainrate.status: 10.1mm per hour was the peak rain rate recorded today ranking 10th in our overall records.  The storm lasted 11.4 hours and 8.82mm of rain fell.  On 02 September 2025, the rain fell at an exceptional rate, peaking at 27.0mm per hour, the heaviest downpour recorded.  A total of 21.19mm fell over the 15.0 hour storm.
